{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4d33898496","title":"国民党一切布置是打，暂无和平希望","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a9fff9bc22","index":0,"year":1946,"month":6,"day":25,"articleId":"4d33898496","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji4","name":"毛泽东文集第四卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"/books/wenji4.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji4":{"comments":[{"id":"de160d5c09","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"4d33898496","publication":{},"article":{},"index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"根据毛泽东手稿刊印。"},{"id":"933a1bd8be","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"4d33898496","publication":{},"article":{},"index":1,"part_index":1,"offset":1,"text":"林，指林彪，当时任东北民主联军总司令兼政治委员。"},{"id":"0d17357a1d","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"4d33898496","publication":{},"article":{},"index":2,"part_index":2,"offset":2,"text":"指中共中央东北局一九四六年六月二十四日给中央的电报。电报说：我们考虑不能将白城子、哈尔滨、佳木斯、牡丹江、安东（今丹东）给国民党驻兵。与其立即交出以上地点，不如在长期战争中力求保持。为打破国民党在战略上的各个击破，彼如集中力量打东北，则我应在华北、华中发动大攻势，给彼以大破坏，迫其停战，这是求得全面停战的最有效方法。目前国民党在东北已外强中干，其在外交上对我之苛刻要求，带有吓唬性质，我不可轻易让步。蒋介石如继续增兵东北，进行战争，则除非是准备全国破裂、与苏联冲突，或已把握苏绝不致干涉。如决心全国内战，则除非已取得美国援助其大规模内战的保证。我们固然要基本上准备作战，但同时应力争和平，作一定限度的让步。"},{"id":"80369ce6af","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"4d33898496","publication":{},"article":{},"index":3,"part_index":3,"offset":24,"text":"指苏联。"}],"contents":[{"id":"3e7fbc5f53","type":"title","text":"国民党一切布置是打，暂无和平希望","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"4d33898496","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"933a1bd8be","type":"appellation","text":"林：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"4d33898496","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0d17357a1d","type":"paragraph","text":"敬电悉。（一）国民党一切布置是打，暂时无和平希望。（二）谈判破裂，全国大打，不限于东北。（三）全靠自力更生。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"4d33898496","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"80369ce6af","type":"subdate","text":"（四）半年至一年内如我打胜，和平有望。（五）友邦在将来","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"4d33898496","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"76039a1d8d","type":"paragraph","text":"可能在外交上给以援助。（六）我党在南京谈判中，当尽最后努力，付出最大让步，以求妥协，但你们不要幻想。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"4d33898496","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9496ffed91","type":"paragraph","text":"中央","index":5,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"4d33898496","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dbca4b0564","type":"paragraph","text":"巳有","index":6,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"4d33898496","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":148,"end":148}}}},"__N_SSG":true}